  "title": "Clinic Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Full Time/ Part - Time Customer Service Officer Cum Herbal Medication Dispenser</p><p>Job scope and responsibilities:</p><p>• Manage reception area.</p><p>• Attend to patients and perform front-desk duties such as patient registration, appointment making, billing, etc.</p><p>• Administrative duties such as insurance claims, etc.</p><p>• Herbal dispensing, packing and stock taking.</p><p>• Assist TCM physician during consultations if required.</p><p>• Maintenance of hygiene and cleanliness of clinic.</p><p>• Any other duties as required.</p><p>Requirements</p><p>• Experience in healthcare setting would be an advantage.</p><p>• Good interpersonal and communication skills</p><p>• Good customer-service mindset</p><p>• 5.5 day work week (may include evening sessions and/or weekends)</p>",
